template<typename KEY, typename VALUE, typename PAIR_TRAITS, typename TRAITS, class ALLOCATOR>
template<typename VALUE_REF>
class cds::ordered_list::LazyList< gc::no_gc, KEY, VALUE, PAIR_TRAITS, TRAITS, ALLOCATOR >::NonConcurrentIterator< VALUE_REF >

Non-concurrent iterator.

This iterator is not thread safe. Template parameter VALUE_REF defines type of iterator return value (const or not)
